\f0\b\fs20 \cf0 Problem Title: 
\f1\b0 Soil Degradation, Pests, and Diseases\

\f0\b Problem Bullets:
\f1\b0 \
\'95 Higher temperatures and drought conditions
\f0\b \'a0are correlated with\'a0\cf3 \ul \ulc3 significantly lower\cf0 \ulnone \'a0({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.icpac.net/media/documents/Banana_Yields__Climate_Change.pdf"}}{\fldrslt https://www.icpac.net/media/documents/Banana_Yields__Climate_Change.pdf}}) banana yields.
\f1\b0 \
