\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 SOLUTION DESCRIPTION
\f1\b0\fs32 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-1\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs20 \cf0 Solution Title: 
\f1\b0 IITA\'92s Climate Smart Package\

\f0\b Solution Bullets:
\f1\b0 \
\'95 
\f0\b Advanced Seed Technologies
\f1\b0 . Seed varieties that are resistant to disease and drought: The {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://e-catalogs.taat-africa.org/gov/technologies?search=&commodities%255B%255D=Banana%252FPlantain&sort_order=0%22%20%5Ct%20%22_blank"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 Kabana 6H/NARITA 7 hybrid}}\cf3 \ul \ulc3  ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://e-catalogs.taat-africa.org/com/technologies/kabana-6hnarita7-hybrid-high-yielding-and-disease-tolerant-banana"}}{\fldrslt https://e-catalogs.taat-africa.org/com/technologies/kabana-6hnarita7-hybrid-high-yielding-and-disease-tolerant-banana}})\cf0 \ulnone \'a0seed and NARITA 17. Leveraging in-vitro banana tissue culture propagation.\
\'95 
\f0\b Agronomic Innovations. 
\f1\b0 Evidence-based intercropping technologies: intercropping banana and plantain plants with cassava, legumes, yams, and coffee increases yield and restores soil health.\
\'95 
\f0\b Digital Tools for Implementation and Management. 
\f1\b0 Use the BXW App to monitor Banana Wilt Disease. Available on the Google Play store. Establish community-based seed multiplication systems for sustainable access\
\'95 
\f0\b Our Team of Experts. 
\f1\b0 Experts like Rony Sweenen, who has been researching bananas in Africa for 50 years, to support your implementation. \
